All drivers and test files are tested on lubuntu 18.04 system.

Each cases are provided in different folders.

For each folder, type command in terminal: make all

Then:
sudo insmod driver_case<i>.ko
sudo ./case<i>

To run the test program using driver provided.

Deadlock will be encountered for each case test file. When testing each case, driver must be loaded again using the 
corresponding driver for each case.

Code review is provided under this directory.